metadata.name: "Content" Condor Gold (Iconics 1/1)
metadata.description:
*VeeFriends Iconics* - Created By [VeeFriends](https://veefriends.com)  

*VeeFriends Iconics* is a collection of 1 of 1 NFTs featuring the VeeFriends Series 1 Spectacular characters. 

Holders of VeeFriends Series 1 Spectaculars (Bubble Gum, Diamond, Gold, Hologram, & Lava) received this commemorative token as part of the launch of VeeFriends Series 2 on April 15, 2022, a signature event in the evolution of VeeFriends Characters. Each Spectacular was reimagined in veteran NFT artist [Gilang Bogy's](https://gilangbogy.com) signature fractured WPAP style.

Additionally, each original owner of this NFT was eligible to claim one free 12"x12" [Metarelics](https://www.metarelics.co/) canvas print of their NFT. 

This token is a [VeeFriends Iconics](https://opensea.io/collection/veefriends-iconics) collectible that lives on the Ethereum blockchain.

[VeeFriends Iconics High Resolution Artwork File](https://media.veefriends.com/image/upload/v1661532558/veefriends/specials/spectacular-drop/high-res/content-condor-gold.jpg)
